{
  "page": "Lord Steffon's tourney",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Ilich_Heariquez_Storm%27s_End_Tourney_Grounds.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7c/Ilich_Heariquez_Storm%27s_End_Tourney_Grounds.JPG/400px-Ilich_Heariquez_Storm%27s_End_Tourney_Grounds.JPG\" width=\"400\" height=\"257\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/7/7c/Ilich_Heariquez_Storm%27s_End_Tourney_Grounds.JPG 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Ilich_Heariquez_Storm%27s_End_Tourney_Grounds.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Storm's End Tourney Grounds, by Ilich Henriquez © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Lord Steffon's tourney</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> was held at <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> possibly between <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_278_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">278&#160;AC</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a>, after the <a href=\"/index.php/Defiance_of_Duskendale\" title=\"Defiance of Duskendale\">Defiance of Duskendale</a> and before <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Contradictions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Contradictions</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Joust\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Joust</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Steffon%27s_tourney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> recounts to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> that her brother, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar</a> once rode brilliantly in a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>, defeating Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Baratheon\" title=\"Steffon Baratheon\">Steffon Baratheon</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Mallister\" title=\"Jason Mallister\">Jason Mallister</a>, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a> who turned out to be <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Toyne\" title=\"Simon Toyne\">Simon Toyne</a>, and, after breaking twelve lances, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a>. However, Rhaegar was defeated by a knight of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> in the champion's tilt.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Hightower\" title=\"Gerold Hightower\">Gerold Hightower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a>, wrote in Barristan's <a href=\"/index.php/White_Book\" title=\"White Book\">White Book</a> entry that Lord Steffon's tourney took place at Storm's End, in which Barristan was named champion after unhorsing Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a>, Prince Oberyn, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leyton_Hightower\" title=\"Leyton Hightower\">Leyton Hightower</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a>, Lord Jason, and Prince Rhaegar Targaryen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Contradictions\">Contradictions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Steffon%27s_tourney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Contradictions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Based on semi-canon sources, the tourney at Storm's End mentioned by Barristan and Lord Steffon's tourney are the same event, with the unnamed knight who defeated Rhaegar in the first account being actually Barristan, who didn't want to bring attention to himself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> However, there are discrepancies between Barristan's recollection and Gerold Hightower's report. While Barristan tells Daenerys that Oberyn Martell and Jason Mallister were defeated by Rhaegar, the White Book states that they were defeated by Barristan himself. Furthermore, Barristan says that Rhaegar defeated Simon Toyne, but the White Book entry lists the tourneys at <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> and Storm's End after the vanquishing of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">Kingswood Brotherhood</a>, during which Barristan killed Simon. In addition to that, the White Book entry calls the event \"Lord Steffon's tourney\" and at the same time names Robert Baratheon \"lord\", implying Steffon was dead at the time of the tourney, whereas Barristan recounts that Steffon took part in the hastilude.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>, the White Book is correct, while Barristan Selmy misremembered several details of the hastilude, conflating circumstances that happened at two or three different tourneys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> With respect to some potential inconsistencies in the White Book's entry, Gerold Hightower may have listed Barristan's tourneys and the fight in the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood\" title=\"Kingswood\">Kingswood</a> not in a chronological order, which means that Simon Toyne may have actually competed against Rhaegar at Storm's End. Moreover, it is possible that the tourney was held after Steffon's death, in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_278_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">278&#160;AC</a> or early <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_279_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">279&#160;AC</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf417.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf417.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and that the new lord Robert named it after the late lord as a homage to his own father. That would be consistent with Robert taking part in the joust, since in 278 AC he <a href=\"/index.php/Customs#Age_of_majority\" title=\"Customs\">came of age</a>, the time after which most <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> receive their knighthoods,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf417.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf417.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> as well as with Toyne's death in <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Steffon%27s_tourney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>As reported by <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Hightower\" title=\"Gerold Hightower\">Gerold Hightower</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/White_Book\" title=\"White Book\">White Book</a>:<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Selmy\" title=\"House Selmy\"><img alt=\"House Selmy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/32px-House_Selmy.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/48px-House_Selmy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/64px-House_Selmy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/32px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/48px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/64px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Selmy\" title=\"House Selmy\"><img alt=\"House Selmy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/32px-House_Selmy.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/48px-House_Selmy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/64px-House_Selmy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/32px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/48px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/64px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> defeated Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Selmy\" title=\"House Selmy\"><img alt=\"House Selmy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/32px-House_Selmy.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/48px-House_Selmy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/64px-House_Selmy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/32px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/48px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/64px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leyton_Hightower\" title=\"Leyton Hightower\">Leyton Hightower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Selmy\" title=\"House Selmy\"><img alt=\"House Selmy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/32px-House_Selmy.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/48px-House_Selmy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/64px-House_Selmy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\"><img alt=\"House Connington.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/32px-House_Connington.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/48px-House_Connington.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/64px-House_Connington.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Selmy\" title=\"House Selmy\"><img alt=\"House Selmy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/32px-House_Selmy.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/48px-House_Selmy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/64px-House_Selmy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mallister\" title=\"House Mallister\"><img alt=\"House Mallister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/32px-House_Mallister.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/48px-House_Mallister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/64px-House_Mallister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Mallister\" title=\"Jason Mallister\">Jason Mallister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Selmy\" title=\"House Selmy\"><img alt=\"House Selmy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/32px-House_Selmy.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/48px-House_Selmy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/House_Selmy.svg/64px-House_Selmy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> defeated Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a></li></ul>\n<p>According to Barristan Selmy, Rhaegar Targaryen defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Baratheon\" title=\"Steffon Baratheon\">Steffon Baratheon</a>, Lord Jason Mallister, Prince Oberyn Martell, <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Toyne\" title=\"Simon Toyne\">Simon Toyne</a>, disguised as a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a>, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> However, Barristan's account is unreliable, since he confused events that happened at different tourneys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Steffon%27s_tourney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7